    <description>A race of floating psychic serpents whose semblance evokes ancient legends. They possess an intense innate sensitivity to psychics and the instinctive drive to affect the psychic field without conscious effort. 

Few could answer to the nature of their origins, some speculating them to be an ancient living weapon. Some still question the scope of the creature's intelligence, regarding their feral dispositions as pre-sapient in nature.

Flight seems to come effortlessly to them in the form of a psychic anti-gravitational force. The spade-ended tendrils beneath are seldom used for locomotion, instead reserved for intelligent manipulation and as deadly serrated weapons.</description>
